General.Name: X2M Connect Ltd
General.Description: X2M Connect Limited, a technology company, provides Internet of Things business technology for the utility sector in the Asia-Pacific. It offers a technology that connects various devices over the internet, such as water meters and gas pressure sensors, and enables data exchange and control of devices. X2M Connect Limited was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Mount Waverley, Australia.
